食左三個月高左1cm所以都想試</blockquote><br />\n1cm可能誤算啫，企個身直啲，個頭岳高少少，對鞋底厚啲，個頭gel高啲都得啦"},{"pid":"f31b58a1b1f603866adc89fa8081a678f4f2c060","tid":433003,"uid":37413,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-12T06:06:00.000Z","msg":"咁都信，有冇常識<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5f3b05facb5333186de59b7c3513a7c93a7649fa","tid":433003,"uid":35420,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-12T07:23:23.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>175》184<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n咁多 我都係162---&gt;168咋喎<br />\n你食咩牌子 食左幾耐</blockquote><br />\n好野梗係唔講比人知<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 個個米八仲得了<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 總要有人做矮仔<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/09.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"599e26a23b27e5f728909edadc7e4c740de98502","tid":433003,"uid":126447,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-22T05:54:17.000Z","msg":"25歲 169.5食左三個月無高 以為無用 <br />\n點知第5個月一度 174 呢家準備再入 <br />\n但好貴"},{"pid":"3f6f8047619de4012ceeeca60c4de63d79d85c09","tid":433003,"uid":74497,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-22T05:57:07.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 堅係有效,不過要食唔少<br />\n利伸:26, 165&gt;178"},{"pid":"8348140b835179b642dbb5ef0d333ff52a94cb02","tid":433003,"uid":126447,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-22T06:01:00.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 堅係有效,不過要食唔少<br />\n利伸:26, 165&gt;178</blockquote><br />\n13cm 有無呀 我得4.5 cm"},{"pid":"aa1dbb97997bd764a030e97e4ab1c24a10f2ca20","tid":433003,"uid":152934,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy"